General.Name: Aventura Group AB Series B
General.Description: Aventura Group AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, operates as an e-commerce and brand accelerator in China. The company serves brands in various categories, including fashion, beauty, wellness, and accessories, etc. Aventura Group AB (publ) was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden with additional offices in Shanghai and Hong Kong.
